{"id": 2904, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今你对生活的信任都体现在哪些小事上？", "description": "日常中，你都是怎么表现“人与人之间基本的信任”的？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Printstock）", "record_count": 2410, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190418235644utLqvTGzxSUf8Nbm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-22T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 343811, "content": "外卖放宿舍门口", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508716}, {"id": 340492, "content": "点外卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901471}, {"id": 340748, "content": "在淘宝京东上买酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128392}, {"id": 340493, "content": "考试虐我千百遍，对它依旧如初恋。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954596}, {"id": 340495, "content": "不瞎翻别人的手机，包括男友的。即便拥有对方的社交账号密码也不登录", "image": null, "praise_count": 286, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635421}, {"id": 340751, "content": "约定好见面时间，准时出现", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644118}, {"id": 340496, "content": "把伞放学校图书馆门口，不怕别人拿走。", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1597073}, {"id": 340497, "content": "朋友圈没有设置三天或半年可见", "image": null, "praise_count": 225, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633518}, {"id": 340498, "content": "可以背包进超市", "image": null, "praise_count": 420, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963421}, {"id": 340499, "content": "不翻看别人几年前的社交动态", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201899}, {"id": 340500, "content": "家里没人  快递放门口", "image": null, "praise_count": 228, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978756}, {"id": 340501, "content": "聊天时候，向对方发送手机截屏，代表我信任这个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 136, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283400}, {"id": 340502, "content": "对朋友圈没有任何限制，因为：\n我不发朋友圈😀", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 340503, "content": "出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525237}, {"id": 340504, "content": "快递，外卖放在门口，等回家再取", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136606}, {"id": 340505, "content": "合租", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415436}, {"id": 340506, "content": "不肩窥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453774}, {"id": 340507, "content": "在公共空间不回避他人的搭讪，乐意与其聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216372}, {"id": 340508, "content": "约炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665111}, {"id": 342556, "content": "父母朋友可以解锁我的手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648575}, {"id": 340509, "content": "可以互相玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868692}, {"id": 340510, "content": "老师会把作业和答案同时发给我们", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628980}, {"id": 340511, "content": "能安静的躺着让澡堂师傅搓背", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641762}, {"id": 340512, "content": "上了出租车就睡觉，当然不建议这么做", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557775}, {"id": 340513, "content": "在合租公寓的冰箱里放各种零食、饮料、冰淇淋", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484562}, {"id": 340515, "content": "不翻别人东西，别人不在不用动别人东西，更不要拿，不管关系多好", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637829}, {"id": 340516, "content": "某网发了有删的文章。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404895}, {"id": 340517, "content": "手机相册随你翻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132585}, {"id": 340518, "content": "买到正品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 340521, "content": "被骗的太多次了 该怎么相信", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310565}, {"id": 340522, "content": "不随意翻看他人手机或者登录对方社交账号，不管是恋人还是朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494663}, {"id": 340523, "content": "打电话或者接电话时，不介意旁边有人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277877}, {"id": 340524, "content": "和微信上的陌生人买东西时，没有选择货到付款", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643522}, {"id": 340525, "content": "日常每天开开心心一鸡蛋", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1636782}, {"id": 340526, "content": "不愿意对这个社会有一丝丝敌意与防备 然而不可能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578044}, {"id": 340527, "content": "到付", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 340528, "content": "不翻老公和宝宝的的手机和包以及衣服口袋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590940}, {"id": 340530, "content": "不戴套", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467319}, {"id": 340531, "content": "将电脑手机都放在图书馆里然后去吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643559}, {"id": 342068, "content": "朋友圈、QQ空间、微博等等对所有人可见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630528}, {"id": 342069, "content": "手机没密码，空间和朋友圈所有人可见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630528}, {"id": 340535, "content": "除了诈骗短信和骚扰电话，大部分都是信任的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775953}, {"id": 340541, "content": "先吃饭后付款", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936746}, {"id": 340806, "content": "过安检", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641677}, {"id": 340553, "content": "不催债，也不被催债", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412266}, {"id": 340560, "content": "取钱不再带保镖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318790}, {"id": 340561, "content": "愿意相信的时候什么都会信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215281}, {"id": 340817, "content": "贵重物品放在工作室 不担心有人拿走", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644247}, {"id": 340562, "content": "穿拖鞋下楼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643598}, {"id": 340572, "content": "前后对比一致", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634591}]}